FADE IN:

INT. DINER - NIGHT

A diner. DETECTIVE MILLER is talking to JANE, a waitress.

DETECTIVE MILLER
You saw the man leave?

JANE
Yes. He was running.

DETECTIVE MILLER
Did you know him?

JANE
No.

DETECTIVE MILLER
Are you sure?

JANE
(nervous)
I'm sure.

DETECTIVE MILLER
We'll be in touch.

He leaves. Jane watches him.

FADE OUT.

